item.description: This walk is part of a national effort (Coast to Coast Bully Walk) to honor bully breed dogs and denounce breed specific legislation. It will be held on Pit Bull Awareness Day at 10:45am in Wakefield, MA, at the north end of Lake Quannapowitt (exit 39 off rte 128), starting at Quannapowitt Pkwy. Well-managed dogs of any breed on leashes are cordially invited to the walk, conversely you do not have to bring a dog in order to participate.
item.name: Coast to Coast Bully Walk - Eastern MA
